<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-49-0748 </DOCNO><TEXT>The text of a press conference given by the NRPB in November 1987 concerningrisk estimates associated with exposure to ionising radiation is presented.Following the re-assessment of fatal cancer risk estimates in the survivorsof the atomic bombs at Hiroshima and Nagasaki, the NRPB are advisingthat an increase of a factor of two or three should be anticipated forradiation protection purposes.</TEXT></DOC>